 1999-11271999-06-170,  AGRI-FOOD,  TB,  ,  ,  ,  , 
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to implement the CANADIAN RURAL PARTNERSHIP INITIATIVE - PHASE II, which includes the entry into Contribution Agreements with individuals and organizations for the purposes of community development in rural areas, undertaking collaborative and inter-institutional research, and the development of a strategic action plan to address rural priorities.
